; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 319-321
; Tests the fixated price annotation path ({=price}) with both plain virtual
; postings (that don't must_balance) and balanced virtual postings.
; When fixated prices trigger balance recomputation, non-must-balance and
; balanced-virtual postings should be skipped during the recompute loop.

2024/01/01 Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage           10 AAPL {=$150.00}
    Assets:Cash              $-1500.00
    (Memo:Purchase)           $1500.00
    [Budget:Investments]      $1500.00
    [Budget:Cash]

test bal
           $-1500.00
             10 AAPL  Assets
             10 AAPL    Brokerage
           $-1500.00    Cash
                   0  Budget
           $-1500.00    Cash
            $1500.00    Investments
            $1500.00  Memo:Purchase
--------------------
             10 AAPL
end test
